# Place your Google Analytics service account JSON file here.
# Name it google-analytics-credentials.json
#
# How to get this file:
# 1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 2. Create a project (or use an existing one)
# 3. Enable "Google Analytics Admin API" and "Google Analytics Data API"
# 4. Go to "Credentials" -> "Service Accounts" -> create or use existing
# 5. Download the JSON key file and rename it to this
# 6. Share your GA4 property with the service account email
#
# See: docs/GOOGLE-ANALYTICS-SETUP.md for full step-by-step instructions